    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="transcript" id="P96-80">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>A light exists in spring</l>
                    <l>Not present on the year</l>
                    <l>At any other period.</l>
                    <l>When March is scarcely here</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>A color stands abroad</l>
                    <l>On solitary hills</l>
                    <l>That science cannot overtake,</l>
                    <l>But human nature feels.</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>It waits upon the lawn;</l>
                    <l>It shows the furthest tree</l>
                    <l>Upon the furthest slope we know;</l>
                    <l>It almost speaks to me.</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Then, as horizons step,</l>
                    <l>Or noons report away,</l>
                    <l>Without the formula of sound,</l>
                    <l>It passes, and we stay:</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>A quality of loss</l>
                    <l>Affecting our content,</l>
                    <l>As trade had suddenly encroached</l>
                    <l>Upon a sacrament.</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
